snippet.title: Shores of Plunder - Early Access Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Avast ye! Welcome aboard to the ultimate pirate adventure in SHORES OF PLUNDER! Battle friends, outlast hoards of enemies, and amass the greatest fortune in the seven seas. Race against time on a dangerous island filled with treasure, then unwind in a secret pirate cove full of shenanigans.

Early Access launching December 5th, 2023
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1567190/Shores_of_Plunder/
